1.text: Clean your face of any previous makeup.
1.vid: /a/a4/Apply Makeup for a Natural Look Step 1 Version 4.360p.mp4

2.text: Apply concealer to any blemishes and around your eyes.
2.vid: /0/0e/Apply Makeup for a Natural Look Step 3 Version 7.360p.mp4

3.text: Apply a powder foundation on the oilier parts of your face.
3.vid: /9/9f/Apply Makeup for a Natural Look Step 4 Version 7.360p.mp4

4.vid: /7/7f/Apply Makeup for a Natural Look Step 5 Version 8.360p.mp4

5.vid: /c/c8/Apply Makeup for a Natural Look Step 6 Version 8.360p.mp4

6.text: Line your upper lashline with a brown, black or gray kohl pencil.
6.vid: /3/30/Apply Makeup for a Natural Look Step 7 Version 7.360p.mp4

7.text: Use a white eyeliner to make your eyes look larger.
7.vid: /0/08/Apply Makeup for a Natural Look Step 8 Version 7.360p.mp4

8.vid: /1/1d/Apply Makeup for a Natural Look Step 9 Version 8.360p.mp4

9.vid: /0/09/Apply Makeup for a Natural Look Step 10 Version 8.360p.mp4

10.text: Apply a sheer nude lip color.
10.vid: /8/8a/Apply Makeup for a Natural Look Step 11 Version 5.360p.mp4

11.text: Dab a tiny amount of the shimmering blush onto the center of your lips.
11.vid: /b/bf/Apply Makeup for a Natural Look Step 12 Version 7.360p.mp4

12.text: Enjoy your dewy, fresh, radiant look.
